79705>>>>>Define vCSIDL_FLAG_CREATE       For |CI$8000 // IE5+, use this to create a special folder
79705>>>>>Define vCSIDL_ADMIN_TOOLS       For |CI$0030 // IE5+, The file system directory that is used to store administrative tools for an individual user
79705>>>>>Define vCSIDL_ALT_STARTUP       For |CI$001D // The file system directory that corresponds to the user's nonlocalized Startup program group
