81086>>>>>    Function DataSources Returns String
81088>>>>>        Local String  sDriver
81088>>>>>        Local String  sDataSource
81088>>>>>        Local String  sDescription
81088>>>>>        Local Integer iLength
81088>>>>>        Local Integer iRetval
81088>>>>>
81088>>>>>        Get psDriverID To sDriver
81089>>>>>        If (sDriver <> "") Begin
81091>>>>>            Move 8192 To iLength
81092>>>>>            Move (Repeat(" ", iLength)) To sDataSource
81093>>>>>            Move (Repeat(" ", iLength)) To sDescription
81094>>>>>            Call_Driver 0 sDRiver Function CLI_DATASOURCES Callback 0 Passing sDataSource sDescription iLength Result iRetval
81099>>>>>        End
81099>>>>>>
81099>>>>>
81099>>>>>        If (sDataSource <> "" Or sDescription <> "") ;            Function_Return (sDataSource + "," +  sDescription)
81102>>>>>        Else ;            Function_Return ""
81104>>>>>    End_Function// DataSources
