Including file: Base64Functions.pkg    (C:\Projects\DF18\DbUpdateFramework\AppSrc\Base64Functions.pkg)
81335>>>>>>>>>//> This package enables base64 encoding and decoding of strings:
81335>>>>>>>>>//>
81335>>>>>>>>>//>     Get EncodeString of oBase64Functions sValue to sValue
81335>>>>>>>>>//>     Get DecodeString of oBase64Functions sValue to sValue
81335>>>>>>>>>//>
81335>>>>>>>>>//> Remember to set the "max argument size" if dealing with very large
81335>>>>>>>>>//> strings.
81335>>>>>>>>>//>
81335>>>>>>>>>//> For 17.1 and later the functionality of this package is based on two functions (Base64Encode and
81335>>>>>>>>>//> Base64Decode) that are built into the runtime.
81335>>>>>>>>>//>
81335>>>>>>>>>//> But for versions up to and including 17.0 it's based on the vdfBase64.dll file that was obtained
81335>>>>>>>>>//> from DAE that have kindly allowed me to distribute it to other DF developers. Programs including
81335>>>>>>>>>//> this package will give off an error on start-up if vdfBase64.dll is not found in the /bin folder
81335>>>>>>>>>//> if the VDF runtime. You will find the DLL in the /programs folder of the StureApsPublicLib workspace
81335>>>>>>>>>
81335>>>>>>>>>Use VdfBase.pkg
81335>>>>>>>>>
81335>>>>>>>>>// Functions in vdfBase64.dll
81335>>>>>>>>>External_Function xxBase64Encode "vdfbase64Encode" vdfBase64.dll Pointer pBuffer Returns Integer
81336>>>>>>>>>External_Function xxBase64Decode "vdfbase64Decode" vdfBase64.dll Pointer pBuffer Returns Integer
81337>>>>>>>>>External_Function xxBase64Free   "vdfbase64Free"   vdfBase64.dll Pointer pBuffer Returns Integer
81338>>>>>>>>>
81338>>>>>>>>>// Structure
81338>>>>>>>>>Struct txxfBase64Buffer
81338>>>>>>>>>    Pointer pData
81338>>>>>>>>>    Integer iLength
81338>>>>>>>>>End_Struct 
81338>>>>>>>>>
81338>>>>>>>>>Global_Variable Integer oBase64Functions
81338>>>>>>>>>
81338>>>>>>>>>Object _oBase64Functions is a cObject
81340>>>>>>>>>    Move Self to oBase64Functions
81341>>>>>>>>>
81341>>>>>>>>>
81341>>>>>>>>>    Function EncodeString String sValue Returns String
81344>>>>>>>>>        Address pBase64
81344>>>>>>>>>        String sResult
81344>>>>>>>>>        Integer iVoid
81344>>>>>>>>>        Move (Base64Encode(AddressOf(sValue), Length(sValue))) to pBase64
81345>>>>>>>>>        Move pBase64 to sResult
81346>>>>>>>>>        Move (Free(pBase64)) to iVoid
81347>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return sResult
81348>>>>>>>>>    End_Function
81349>>>>>>>>>
81349>>>>>>>>>    Function DecodeString String sValue Returns String
81352>>>>>>>>>        Address pBinary
81352>>>>>>>>>        String sBinary
81352>>>>>>>>>        Integer iVoid iLen
81352>>>>>>>>>        Move (Base64Decode(AddressOf(sValue), &iLen)) to pBinary
81353>>>>>>>>>        Move (Repeat(Character(0), iLen)) to sBinary
81354>>>>>>>>>        Move (MemCopy(AddressOf(sBinary), pBinary, iLen)) to iVoid
81355>>>>>>>>>        Move (Free(pBinary)) to iVoid
81356>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return sBinary
81357>>>>>>>>>    End_Function
81358>>>>>>>>>
81358>>>>>>>>>End_Object
