81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Drivers     All
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @VersionNote Last Revised: 2013-07-15 by Oliver Nelson
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @See
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @INTOPT DATABASE_NAME {string}
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>///
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Syntax Get_Attribute DF_FILE_TABLE_NAME of {FileNumber} to {variable}
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Syntax Set_Attribute DF_FILE_TABLE_NAME of {FileNumber} to {variable}
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Param  FileNumber            Number of the file
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Param  variable              Name of the SQL Table.
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Example
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// Open Orderhea
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// Get_Attribute DF_FILE_TABLE_NAME of Orderhea.File_Number to strVal
