81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// To use this: Change the type of a date field in your FD to string type,
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// Set the attribute DF_FIELD_TIME_ON of this field to TRUE and
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// recompile your program.
