81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Name        DF_INDEX_NAME
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Description Use this attribute to get the name of the index on the SQL backend
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// that maps to the numbered index in Dataflex.  This is because, unlike Dataflex,
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// all indexes in SQL are stored as names, not numbers. Since this attribute is
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// currently only a ReadOnly attribute, it can not be used to set or modify a named
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// index.
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>///
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// This is a ReadOnly attribute
