82390>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Name        GET_MAX_OBJECT_NAME_LENGTH
82390>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Description This command returns the maximum length allowed for object
82390>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// names in the SQl backend. This includes table names, column names,
82390>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// database names etc. The maximum length in put into the specified variable.
82390>>>>>>>>>>>>>///
82390>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Assumptions
82390>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Status      Public
