82390>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @VersionNote Last Revised: 2013-10-04 by Aaron Gulack
82390>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @See
82390>>>>>>>>>>>>>///
82390>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Syntax GET_MAX_OBJECT_NAME_LENGTH to {variable}
82390>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Param variable                     Variable to hold the maximum length
82390>>>>>>>>>>>>>///
82390>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Example
82390>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// GET_MAX_OBJECT_NAME_LENGTH to iMaxLength
82390>>>>>>>>>>>>>
