82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @See
82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>///
82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Syntax SQL_GET_MAX_CURSORS_STMT [of {server}] to {variable}
82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Param server                       Name of the server (optional)
82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Param variable                     Maximum number of cursors allowed
82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>///
