84413>>>>>>>>>>>        SQL_GET_PROCEDURE_PARAMETER iArgnum to retval
84437>>>>>>>>>>>>
84437>>>>>>>>>>>
84437>>>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return retval
84438>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Function
