84539>>>>>>>>>>>    Function SQLConnect String sDriver String sConnect Returns Handle
84541>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap[] maps
84541>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap[] maps
84542>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap conn
84542>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap conn
84542>>>>>>>>>>>        
84542>>>>>>>>>>>        Get ptCLIHandleMaps to maps
84543>>>>>>>>>>>        Move sDriver to conn.sDriver
84544>>>>>>>>>>>        Move sConnect to conn.sConnect
84545>>>>>>>>>>>
84545>>>>>>>>>>>        If (SizeOfArray(maps) > 0) Move (maps[(SizeOfArray(maps)-1)].iHdbc+1) to conn.iHdbc
84548>>>>>>>>>>>        Else Move 1 to conn.iHdbc
84550>>>>>>>>>>>        
84550>>>>>>>>>>>        Set CurrentConnection to sDriver sConnect 
84551>>>>>>>>>>>        If (not(Err)) Begin
84553>>>>>>>>>>>            Move conn to maps[(SizeOfArray(maps))]
84554>>>>>>>>>>>            Set ptCLIHandleMaps to maps
84555>>>>>>>>>>>            Set ptCLIHandleMap to conn
84556>>>>>>>>>>>        End
84556>>>>>>>>>>>>
84556>>>>>>>>>>>        
84556>>>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return Self
