84863>>>>>>>>>>>
84863>>>>>>>>>>>    Function CKMajorRevision Returns Integer
84865>>>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return (ExtractPartFromRevision (Current_Object, 1, CKRevision(Current_Object)))
84866>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Function // CKMajorRevision
84867>>>>>>>>>>>
84867>>>>>>>>>>>
84867>>>>>>>>>>>
