84871>>>>>>>>>>>    //*** Purpose : Returns the release revision of the CK
84871>>>>>>>>>>>    //***
84871>>>>>>>>>>>
84871>>>>>>>>>>>    Function CKReleaseRevision Returns Integer
84873>>>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return (ExtractPartFromRevision (Current_Object, 3, CKRevision(Current_Object)))
