85026>>>>>>>>>        Move iSQLKeywordConstant to SQLKeywordArray[iSize].iSQLWord
85027>>>>>>>>>        Move iEN_dbType          to SQLKeywordArray[iSize].iSQLDbType
85028>>>>>>>>>        Move sSQLKeyword         to SQLKeywordArray[iSize].sSQLPhrase
85029>>>>>>>>>        
85029>>>>>>>>>        Set paSQLKeywordArray to SQLKeywordArray
85030>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure  
