85258>>>>>>>Class cDbUpdateDB2Driver is a cDbUpdateGenericDatabaseDriver
85259>>>>>>>    Function DbLogin String sConnectionString String sServer String sDatabase Boolean bTrusted String sUserID String sPassword Returns Boolean
85261>>>>>>>        Boolean bLoginSuccessful
85261>>>>>>>        String sDriverID 
85261>>>>>>>        
85261>>>>>>>        Move False to Err
85262>>>>>>>        Get psDriverID to sDriverID
85263>>>>>>>        If (not(Uppercase(sServer) contains "DSN")) Begin
85265>>>>>>>            Move ("DSN=" + sServer) to sServer
85266>>>>>>>        End
85266>>>>>>>>
85266>>>>>>>        Login sServer sUserId sPassword sDriverID
85268>>>>>>>        
85268>>>>>>>        Move (not(Err)) to bLoginSuccessful
85269>>>>>>>        Function_Return bLoginSuccessful
85270>>>>>>>    End_Function
85271>>>>>>>End_Class
