85525>>>>>    Function SQLIniFileDeleteAllConnections Returns Boolean
85527>>>>>        Integer iCount 
85527>>>>>        Boolean bExists 
85527>>>>>        String sSection
85527>>>>>        
85527>>>>>        Move False to Err
85528>>>>>        Move 1 to iCount
85529>>>>>        Get psIniSectionName to sSection
85530>>>>>        Get SectionExists (CS_SQLIniSectionName + String(iCount)) to bExists
85531>>>>>        While (bExists = True)
85535>>>>>            Send DeleteSection (CS_SQLIniSectionName + String(iCount))
85536>>>>>            Increment iCount
85537>>>>>            Get SectionExists (CS_SQLIniSectionName + String(iCount)) to bExists
85538>>>>>        Loop
85539>>>>>>
85539>>>>>        Function_Return (Err = False)
85540>>>>>    End_Function
