86880>>>
86880>>>    Function IsMertechDriver String sDriverID Returns Boolean
86882>>>        Boolean bOK   
86882>>>        Move False to bOK
86883>>>            Move (sDriverID = SQLFLEX or sDriverID = ORAFLEX or sDriverID = MDSPgSQL or sDriverID = MDSMYSQL) to bOK
86884>>>        Function_Return bOK
86885>>>    End_Function
