86979>>>        Else Move (Mid(sConnectionString, 1, (iPos +1)))                        to sValue
86981>>>        Move (If(sValue = 1, True, False))                                      to bSilent
86982>>>
86982>>>        Move (Trim(sDriverID))                                                  to SQLConnection.sDriverID
86983>>>        Move (Trim(sConnectionID))                                              to SQLConnection.sConnectionID
86984>>>        Move (Trim(sConnectionString))                                          to SQLConnection.sConnectionString    
