87048>>>//****************************************************************************
87048>>>// $Module type: Class
87048>>>// $Module name: cDbUpdateFunctionLibrary
87048>>>// $Author     : Nils G. Svedmyr, RDC Tools International, <mailto:support@rdctools.com>
87048>>>// Web-site    : http://www.rdctools.com
87048>>>// Created     : 2014-09-05 @ 09:50 (Military date format: YY-MM-DD)
87048>>>//
87048>>>// Description : The class consists of a function library for database manipulations, aka make changes to a database.
87048>>>//               It has top level functions that uses the DataFlex db API, _but_ also specialized
87048>>>//               functions to make db changes to Sql databases with the DAW & Mertech drivers,
87048>>>//               with the help of Sql-scripts.
87048>>>//
87048>>>// $Rev History:
87048>>>//    2014-09-05  Module header created
87048>>>//   
