89506>>>    Function _SqlSelectFromWhereName Returns String
89508>>>        String sRetval sSelect sName sFrom sMaster sSys sDatabases sWhere sDBO
89508>>>        
89508>>>        Get _SqlFindKeyWord CI_SQLSelect       to sSelect
89509>>>        Get _SqlFindKeyWord CI_SQLName         to sName                             
89510>>>        Get _SqlFindKeyWord CI_SQLDBO          to sDBO
