89832>>>    Function _SqlProcedureArrayDAW String sStmt String sArgument Returns String[]
89834>>>        String[] sReturnArray  
89835>>>        String sValue                         
89835>>>        Handle hoSQLHandler hoSQLConnect hStmt    
89835>>>        Integer iRetval iCols iFetchResult
