89836>>>        Get pSQLConnection of ghoSQLConnectionHandler to SQLConnection
89837>>>        Get SqlConnect of hoSQLHandler SQLConnection.sDriverID SQLConnection.sConnectionString to hoSQLConnect
89838>>>
89838>>>        If (hoSQLConnect <> 0) Begin
89840>>>            Get SqlOpen of hoSQLConnect to hStmt
89841>>>            If (hStmt <> 0) Begin
89843>>>                Send SqlSetProcedurename of hStmt sStmt 
89844>>>                If (sArgument <> "") Begin
89846>>>                    Send SqlSetArgument  of hStmt 1 sArgument
89847>>>                End
