89900>>>    Function _SqlDatabasesArrayDB2 Returns String[]
89902>>>        String[] sReturnArray
89903>>>        String sDataSource
89903>>>        Handle hoSQLHandler
89903>>>        Integer iItem
89903>>>
89903>>>        Get phoDB2SQLHandler to hoSQLHandler
89904>>>        Send SeedDataSources of hoSQLHandler
89905>>>
89905>>>        Send Ignore_Error of Error_Object_Id CLIERR_LOGIN_UNSUCCESSFUL
89906>>>
89906>>>        Repeat
89906>>>>
89906>>>            Get DataSources of hoSQLHandler to sDataSource
89907>>>            Move (Replaces(",", sDataSource, "")) to sDataSource
89908>>>            Move (Trim(sDataSource)) to sReturnArray[iItem]
89909>>>            Increment iItem
89910>>>        Until (sDataSource = "")
89912>>>
89912>>>        Send Trap_Error of Error_Object_Id CLIERR_LOGIN_UNSUCCESSFUL
89913>>>
89913>>>        Function_Return sReturnArray
