90279>>>                Case Break
90280>>>            Case (sDriverID = ODBC_DRV_ID)
90283>>>                Case Break
90284>>>            Case (sDriverID = DB2_DRV_ID)
90287>>>                Move SQLConnection.sBaseTableSpace  to sBaseTableSpace
90288>>>                Move SQLConnection.sLongTableSpace  to sLongTableSpace
90289>>>                Move SQLConnection.sIndexTableSpace to sIndexTableSpace
90290>>>                Case Break
