90295>>>                Move SQLConnection.sIndexTableSpace to sIndexTableSpace
90296>>>                Case Break
90297>>>            Case (sDriverID = MDSMySQL) 
90300>>>                Case Break
90301>>>            Case (sDriverID = MDSPgSQL)
90304>>>                Move SQLConnection.sBaseTableSpace  to sBaseTableSpace
90305>>>                Move SQLConnection.sIndexTableSpace to sIndexTableSpace
90306>>>                Case Break  
90307>>>            Case (sDriverID = DATAFLEX_ID)
90310>>>                Case Break
90311>>>            Case Else
