90312>>>>
90312>>>                Case Break
90313>>>        Case End
90313>>>        
90313>>>        Move False to Err   
90314>>>
90314>>>        If (bMertechDriver = True) Begin  
90316>>>            // Note: This function also sets the Err flag.
