94465>>>>>//
94465>>>>>// $File name  : DfAbout.pkg
94465>>>>>// $File title : About class support
94465>>>>>// Notice      :
94465>>>>>// $Author(s)  : Vincent Oorsprong, Ken Ross
94465>>>>>//
94465>>>>>// $Rev History
94465>>>>>//
94465>>>>>// NGS 08/16/2013 Improved by using a cRichEdit object were the params gets added to.
94465>>>>>//                The objects that previously were popupated with values from the params,
94465>>>>>//                and their corresponding "Procedure Set..." messages, were removed as
94465>>>>>//                the edit object is used instead.
94465>>>>>//                The number of params to the DoAbout procedure was increased to ten, so
94465>>>>>//                it is easier to add whatever extra text strings needed/wanted.
94465>>>>>//                The StdAbout.pkg was also changed for this to work. It allows for an extra
94465>>>>>//                five new params to be passed, but these new params are all optional.
94465>>>>>//                So the interface will work exactly as before - if no extra parameters are passed.
94465>>>>>//                Also added an extra bitmap object to show the "Powered By Visual DataFlex" logo, in
94465>>>>>//                the lower left corner of the About object, beneath the "main" About bitmap.
94465>>>>>//                Note: It is assumed that the bitmap "PoweredByVisualDataFlex.bmp" exists.
94465>>>>>//                The background was changed to clWhite for easier usage of bitmaps. Just set the background
94465>>>>>//                color of your bitmap to white and the bitmap will not look jagged.
94465>>>>>//                If an Internet address is passed as one of the params, it will be underlined and clickable.
94465>>>>>//                An e-mail address can also be passed; e.g. "E-mail: mailto:mail@myemailaccount.com" and will
94465>>>>>//                also be clickable.
94465>>>>>// VOO 02/22/2012 Replaced obsolete code, improved Network_User_Name by asking
94465>>>>>//                Windows for the size first.
94465>>>>>// VOO 07/25/2003 Removed OnResize procedure for sysinfo dialog. Replaced logic
94465>>>>>//                with anchor technique. Removed unnessary property in the
94465>>>>>//                sysinfo dialog. Changed the size Of the about & sysinfo dialog
94465>>>>>//                object To better look in Windows XP. Repositioned the close
94465>>>>>//                button in the sysinfo dialog To line up with the display area
94465>>>>>//                Replaced obsolete code and techniques. Removed dead code.
94465>>>>>// JJT 10/23/2001 removed all ghoworkspace support. Uses app object or nothing
94465>>>>>// SWB 07/19/01   Added support Of the Application object in preference to
94465>>>>>//                the global Workspace object, if it is present
94465>>>>>// JJT 11/05/98   Added version information
94465>>>>>// VOO 29/10/98   Replaced the GetFreeSystemResources for the Win32 variant
94465>>>>>// JJT 7/31/97    Registered Enumerate Workspace so dfabout can exist without
94465>>>>>//                workspace package.
94465>>>>>// JJT 6/27/97    Turned the sysinfo objects into classes so the AboutDialog
94465>>>>>//                class can create this object.
94465>>>>>//                Cleaned up the interface (used correct classes and messages)
94465>>>>>//                Added workspace reporting support To sys-info.
94465>>>>>//                Turned off wrapping in the sys-info editor.
94465>>>>>// KR  ??/??/96   File created
94465>>>>>//************************************************************************
