94836>>>>>>>>>>>       String Context
94836>>>>>>>>>>>       If Obj gt 0 ;          Get Help_Context of obj HELP_CONTEXT_ID_OR_KEY to Context
94839>>>>>>>>>>>       if (left(context,1)) in '0123456789' ;          Get System_Help_Context_id Context to Context
94842>>>>>>>>>>>       Send Exec_Context_Help Context
