94856>>>>>>>>>>>    Procedure View_File_Help Integer Obj
94858>>>>>>>>>>>       String Context FilFld
94858>>>>>>>>>>>       Integer File# Field# Dot
94858>>>>>>>>>>>       If Obj gt 0 Begin
94860>>>>>>>>>>>          // This should return the file and field as a string in
94860>>>>>>>>>>>          // FFF.fff format (F=File, f=format).
94860>>>>>>>>>>>          Get Help_Context of Obj HELP_CONTEXT_DATAFILE to FilFld
94861>>>>>>>>>>>          // Parse FilFld into File# and Field#.
94861>>>>>>>>>>>          Pos '.' in FilFld to Dot
94863>>>>>>>>>>>>
94863>>>>>>>>>>>          if Dot ne 0 begin
94865>>>>>>>>>>>             Left FilFld to File#  (dot-1)
94867>>>>>>>>>>>>
94867>>>>>>>>>>>             Mid  FilFld to Field# 255 (dot+1)
94870>>>>>>>>>>>>
94870>>>>>>>>>>>          End
94870>>>>>>>>>>>>
94870>>>>>>>>>>>       End
94870>>>>>>>>>>>>
94870>>>>>>>>>>>       Get System_Help_File_id File# Field# to Context
94871>>>>>>>>>>>       Send Exec_Context_Help Context
94872>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure // View_File_Help
