94875>>>>>>>>>>>        String Context
94875>>>>>>>>>>>        If Obj gt 0 ;           Get Help_Context of obj HELP_CONTEXT_ERROR to Context
94878>>>>>>>>>>>        if (left(context,1)) in '0123456789' ;           Get System_Help_Error_id Context to Context
94881>>>>>>>>>>>        Send Exec_Context_Help Context
94882>>>>>>>>>>>    end_procedure
