94991>>>>>    // Augmented class message to adjust certain text strings that are wrong...
94991>>>>>
94991>>>>>    Procedure AppendTextLn String sText
94993>>>>>        String sWorkspaceWSFile
94993>>>>>
94993>>>>>        // Only works for English:
94993>>>>>        If (ghoApplication > 0) Begin
94995>>>>>            If (sText contains "Workspace Name") Begin
94997>>>>>                Move "Workspace Config Filename:" to sText
94998>>>>>                Get psWorkspaceWSFile of (phoWorkspace(ghoApplication)) to sWorkspaceWSFile
94999>>>>>                Move (sText * sWorkspaceWSFile) to sText
95000>>>>>            End
95000>>>>>>
95000>>>>>        End
95000>>>>>>
95000>>>>>        Send AppendText sText
95001>>>>>        Send AppendText (character(10))
95002>>>>>    End_Procedure
