95067>>>>>
95067>>>>>    Procedure Show_Date_Format
95069>>>>>        Integer iDateFormat
95069>>>>>        String sDateFormat
95069>>>>>
95069>>>>>        Get_Attribute DF_DATE_FORMAT to iDateFormat
95072>>>>>        Case Begin
95072>>>>>            Case (iDateFormat = DF_DATE_USA)
95074>>>>>                Move C_$USA To sDateFormat
95075>>>>>                Case Break
95076>>>>>            Case (iDateFormat = DF_DATE_EUROPEAN)
95079>>>>>                Move C_$European To sDateFormat
95080>>>>>                Case Break
95081>>>>>            Case (iDateFormat = DF_DATE_MILITARY)
95084>>>>>                Move C_$Military To sDateFormat
95085>>>>>                Case Break
95086>>>>>            Case Else
95086>>>>>                Move C_$UnknownDateType To sDateFormat
95087>>>>>                Case Break
95088>>>>>        Case End
95088>>>>>
95088>>>>>        Send AppendTextLn (SFormat (C_$DateFormat, sDateformat))
95089>>>>>    End_Procedure
