95944>>>>>>>        Get pbAutoSearch to bAutoSearch
95945>>>>>>>        If bAutoSearch Begin
95947>>>>>>>            // this can get called multiple times before a search dialog pops up
95947>>>>>>>            Get piLastKey to iKeyCode
95948>>>>>>>            Get piLastKey2 to iShiftCode
95949>>>>>>>            Send AddToSearchKeys iKeyCode iShiftCode
95950>>>>>>>        End
95950>>>>>>>>
95950>>>>>>>        Move True to llCancel
95951>>>>>>>    End_Procedure  // OnComRequestEdit
