96549>>>>>
96549>>>>>        Forward Send Page iPageObject
96551>>>>>
96551>>>>>        If (iPageObject) Begin
96553>>>>>            Get Window_Handle to hWnd
96554>>>>>            If (hWnd) Begin
96556>>>>>                Move (SendMessage(hWnd, WM_QUERYUISTATE, 0, 0)) to iRet
96557>>>>>                If (iRet iand UISF_HIDEFOCUS) Begin
96559>>>>>                    Move (UIS_CLEAR + (UISF_HIDEFOCUS * 65536)) to iState
96560>>>>>                    Move (SendMessage(hWnd, WM_UPDATEUISTATE, iState, 0)) to iRet
96561>>>>>                End
96561>>>>>>
96561>>>>>            End
96561>>>>>>
96561>>>>>        End
96561>>>>>>
96561>>>>>    End_Procedure
