97407>>>>>        Boolean bState
97407>>>>>        
97407>>>>>        Broadcast Recursive Send WriteConnectionData (&sConnectionData)
97409>>>>>        Get pSQLConnectionData to SQLConnectionData
97410>>>>>        Get MoveSQLConnectionToStringArray SQLConnectionData to sConnectionData2
