97498>>>>>            End
97498>>>>>>
97498>>>>>        End
97498>>>>>>
97498>>>>>        
97498>>>>>        Move SQLConnection.sSchema           to sConnectionData[11]
97499>>>>>        Move SQLConnection.sBaseTableSpace   to sConnectionData[12]
97500>>>>>        Move SQLConnection.sLongTableSpace   to sConnectionData[13]
97501>>>>>        Move SQLConnection.sIndexTableSpace  to sConnectionData[14]
97502>>>>>        Move SQLConnection.bSilentLogin      to sConnectionData[15]
97503>>>>>        
97503>>>>>        Function_Return sConnectionData
