97524>>>>>        Move sConnectionData[13] to SQLConnection.sLongTableSpace
97525>>>>>        Move sConnectionData[14] to SQLConnection.sIndexTableSpace
97526>>>>>        Move sConnectionData[15] to SQLConnection.bSilentLogin
97527>>>>>        
97527>>>>>        // Connection string:
97527>>>>>        Get ConstructConnectionString of ghoSQLConnectionHandler SQLConnection.sDriverID SQLConnection.sServer SQLConnection.sDatabase ;                                                                 SQLConnection.bTrusted  SQLConnection.sUserID SQLConnection.sPassword ;                                      to SQLConnection.sConnectionString
97528>>>>>
97528>>>>>        Function_Return SQLConnection
97529>>>>>    End_Function
