97698>>>>>                    Move ("The program was added to the" * sStudioVersion * "Studios Tools menu successfully, but because you installed for an earlier version of the Studio than 16.0 you need to compile the program under that same VDF version, else the Studio can't start the program properly. (Sorry, just a 'feature' of earlier versions of the Studio)") to sText
97699>>>>>                    Break
97700>>>>>            Case End
